A vintage-style holiday scene featuring a wrapped gift box with its lid partially open, revealing glowing XML code brackets and angle symbols floating up like magical sparkles. The gift sits on an old wooden desk surrounded by 1950s-era computing equipment with warm amber vacuum tubes. Falling snow visible through a frosted window in the background. Muted sepia and cream tones with pops of festive red ribbon and green holly accents. Soft bokeh lights create a dreamy, nostalgic atmosphere reminiscent of mid-century advertising illustrations.
